These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-1::.
3 different games are played: bridge, backgammon, poker
The people have 3 different jobs:  videographer, social-worker, firefighter
1. the social-worker is the person playing backgammon##1
2. the person playing poker is between the firefighter and the person playing backgammon##2
3. the person playing bridge is on the right of the videographer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |   3   |
| Game      | backgammon | poker | bridge |
| Job   | social-worker     | videographer    | firefighter   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-2::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: tram, snowmobile, bus
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: february, april, may
1. the person driving the tram is on the left of the person driving the bus##1
2. the person who's birthday is in may is between the person who's birthday is in february and the person driving the tram##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |       2       |       3       |
| Transport   | tram    | bus        | snowmobile |
| Birthday     | april | may | february         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-3::.
There 3 different types of food: lemon, plum, cabbage
There are 3 different nationalities: polish, italian, australian
1. the polish is on the right of the person eating lemon##1
2. the person eating lemon is between the italian and the person eating cabbage##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2     |  3  |
| Food   | plum | lemon     | cabbage |
| Nationality        | italian  | australian | polish |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-4::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: november, august, february
There are 3 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, cola, fanta
1. the person who's birthday is in november is the person drinking almond-milk##1
2. the person who's birthday is in february is between the person drinking cola and the person drinking almond-milk##2
3. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2     |  3   |
| Birthday   | august  | february     | november |
| Beverage           | cola | fanta | almond-milk |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-5::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: ice-hockey, tennis, cycling
The people use 3 different means of transport: bus, tram, train
1. the person who's sport is cycling is on the left of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
2. the person who's sport is cycling is on the right of the person driving the train##1
3. the person driving the bus is between the person driving the train and the person driving the tram##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2      |    3    |
| Sport   | tennis | cycling     | ice-hockey |
| Transport     | train    | bus | tram    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-6::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: country, techno, reggae
There are 3 different favourite colors: pink, white, grey
1. the person who likes pink is between the fan reggae and the fan country##2
2. the fan country is the person who likes white##1
3. the fan techno is on the right of the fan country##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |       3       |
| Music-Genre   | country  | techno   | reggae        |
| Color         | white | pink | grey |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-7::.
3 different pets are kept: mouse, dog, hedgehog
There are 3 different favourite beverages: cola, hot-chocolate, 7up
1. the owner of the hedgehog is on the right of the owner of the mouse##1
2. the person drinking cola is between the owner of the hedgehog and the person drinking hot-chocolate##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |
| Pet          | dog  | mouse  | hedgehog |
| Beverage   | hot-chocolate | cola | 7up     |

