.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-8::.
3 different games are played: snooker, chess, scrabble
House: palace, art-deco, colonial
1. the person playing chess is the colonial house##1
2. the art-deco house is between the person playing chess and the person playing scrabble##2
3. the person playing chess is on the right of the person playing snooker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3    |
| Game   | scrabble   | snooker  | chess  |
| House   | palace | art-deco | colonial |

