.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-9::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: daisy, bellflower, daffodil
There are 3 different favourite colors: pink, red, black
1. the person who likes pink is on the left of the person who growsbellflower##1
2. the person who likes pink is between the person who growsdaffodil and the person who likes red##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |     2      |     3     |
| Flower       | daffodil | daisy | bellflower  |
| Color   | black    | pink        | red |

