.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-10::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: august, july, april
City: nizza, venice, colone
1. the person traveling to nizza is on the right of the person who's birthday is in april##1
2. the person who's birthday is in july is between the person traveling to colone and the person who's birthday is in august##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |   2    |     3     |
| Birthday         | april | july | august |
| City   | colone     | nizza    | venice |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-11::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: western, epic, spy
House: tower, palace, wooden
1. the wooden house is between the person watching epic movies and the tower house##2
2. the person watching spy movies is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |    2     |     3     |
| Movie-Genre   | epic | western      | spy      |
| House       | palace  | wooden | tower |

