.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-12::.
3 different pets are kept: dog, mouse, chinchilla
The people use 3 different means of transport: van, airplane, helicopter
1. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the person driving the van##1
2. the person driving the helicopter is between the person driving the van and the person driving the airplane##2
3. the owner of the dog is on the left of the owner of the mouse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |    3    |
| Pet   | dog | mouse   | chinchilla   |
| Transport         | airplane | helicopter | van |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-13::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: photography, traveling, collecting
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: climbing, tennis, parkour
1. the person who's sport is tennis is on the left of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
2. the person who's sport is parkour is between the person who's sport is climbing and the person who's hobby is photography##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |   2   |     3     |
| Hobby         | photography | traveling  | collecting       |
| Sport   | tennis | parkour | climbing |

