.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-16::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: pink, brown, green
There 3 different types of food: pear, cucumber, lemon
1. the person eating pear is between the person who likes brown and the person who likes green##2
2. the person who likes brown is on the far left##1
3. the person who likes brown is the person eating lemon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |    3     |
| Color   | brown | pink   | green   |
| Food         | lemon  | pear | cucumber |

