.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-20::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  dressmaker, lawyer, nurse
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: iris, azalea, bellflower
1. the dressmaker is on the right of the lawyer##1
2. the lawyer is between the nurse and the person who growsazalea##2
3. the person who growsiris is on the right of the nurse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2   |    3     |
| Job      | nurse | lawyer   | dressmaker |
| Flower   | bellflower  | iris | azalea   |

 